{"lemma":"خَمْرَة","slug":"خَمْرَة","root":"خ.م.ر","root_slug":"خ-م-ر","root_link":"/words/roots/خ-م-ر","pos":"N","pos_camel":"noun","paradigm":[],"frequency_in_corpus":0,"cross_references":{"qac":{"found":false},"wiktextract":{"found":false},"lanes":{"found":true,"entry_ids":["n11478","n11479","n11480","n11481"],"search_url":"https://lanelexicon.com/?s=%D8%AE%D9%8E%D9%85%D9%92%D8%B1%D9%8E%D8%A9"}},"translations":null,"definition":null,"etymology":null,"ipa":null,"lanes_definition":{"source":"lanes","entries":[{"entry_id":"n11478","headword_ar":"خَمْرَةٌ","root":"xmr","body":[{"kind":"text","text":": see"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"xamorN","text_ar":"خَمْرٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":", in two places. ―         -b2-  Also, (S, A, K,) and ↓"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"ximorapN","text_ar":"خِمْرَةٌ","orth_type":"arrow"},{"kind":"text","text":"(Kr, K) and ↓"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"xumorapN","text_ar":"خُمْرَةٌ","orth_type":"arrow"},{"kind":"text","text":", (K,) The"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"odour"},{"kind":"text","text":"of perfume: (S, A:) or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"a sweet odour:"},{"kind":"text","text":"(K:) and the last signifies also"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"an odour which has infected"},{"kind":"text","text":"("},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"xaAmara","text_ar":"خَامَرَ"},{"kind":"text","text":", i. e."},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"xaAlaTa","text_ar":"خَالَطَ"},{"kind":"text","text":",)"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"a person;"},{"kind":"text","text":"(K;) as also ↓"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"xamarapN","text_ar":"خَمَرَةٌ","orth_type":"arrow"},{"kind":"text","text":". (AZ, K.) You say,"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"wajadotu xamorapa","text_ar":"وَجَدْتُ خَمْرَةَ"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"AlT~iybi","text_ar":"الطِّيبِ"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"I experienced,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"smelt, the odour of the perfume."},{"kind":"text","text":"(S, A.)       -A2-  See also"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"xamarN","text_ar":"خَمَرٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":", in two places."}],"source_refs":["S","A","K","Kr"]},{"entry_id":"n11479","headword_ar":"خُمْرَةٌ","root":"xmr","body":[{"kind":"text","text":": see"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"xamiyrN","text_ar":"خَمِيرٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":", in two places. ―         -b2-  Also a dial. var. of"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"gumorapN","text_ar":"غُمْرَةٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":"[q. v.],"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"A thing"},{"kind":"text","text":"[or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"composition"},{"kind":"text","text":"]"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"which is used as a liniment for beautifying the complexion;"},{"kind":"text","text":"(S;) [the"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"plant called"},{"kind":"text","text":"]"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"waros","text_ar":"وَرْس"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"and certain perfumes which a woman uses as a liniment"},{"kind":"text","text":"(so in the K, or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"applies as a liniment to her face,"},{"kind":"text","text":"as in other lexicons, TA)"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"to beautify her face."},{"kind":"text","text":"(K.)       -A2-"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"Pain, and headache, and annoyance, occasioned by wine"},{"kind":"text","text":"("},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"xamor","text_ar":"خَمْر"},{"kind":"text","text":", for which in some copies of the K we find"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"Hum~aY","text_ar":"حُمَّى"},{"kind":"text","text":"erroneously put, TA); as also ↓"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"xumaArN","text_ar":"خُمَارٌ","orth_type":"arrow"},{"kind":"text","text":": or the"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"intoxication thereof, which has infected"},{"kind":"text","text":"("},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"xaAlaTa","text_ar":"خَالَطَ"},{"kind":"text","text":") ["},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"a person"},{"kind":"text","text":"]; (K;) and so ↓"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"xumaArN","text_ar":"خُمَارٌ","orth_type":"arrow"},{"kind":"text","text":": (TA:) or this latter signifies the"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"remains of intoxication:"},{"kind":"text","text":"(S:) pl. of the former"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"xumarN","text_ar":"خُمَرٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":". (TA.) ―         -b2-  See also"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"xamorapN","text_ar":"خَمْرَةٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":".       -A3-"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"A small pot"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"jar:"},{"kind":"text","text":"and"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"a vessel for leaven."},{"kind":"text","text":"(KL.)       -A4-"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"A small mat,"},{"kind":"text","text":"(S, A, * Mgh, Msb, K,) ["},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"of an oblong shape,"},{"kind":"text","text":"]"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"large enough for a man to prostrate himself upon it,"},{"kind":"text","text":"(Mgh, Msb,)"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"used for that purpose"},{"kind":"text","text":"["},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"in prayer"},{"kind":"text","text":"], (S, A,)"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"made of palm-leaves"},{"kind":"text","text":"(S, K)"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"woven"},{"kind":"text","text":"("},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"turomalu","text_ar":"تُرْمَلُ"},{"kind":"text","text":")"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"with threads"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"strings:"},{"kind":"text","text":"(S:) so called because it veils the ground from the face of the person praying [upon it]: (Zj, * Mgh:) or because its threads or strings are hidden by its palm-leaves. (TA.)"}],"source_refs":["TA","S","Mgh","Msb","A","K"]},{"entry_id":"n11480","headword_ar":"خِمْرَةٌ","root":"xmr","body":[{"kind":"italic_en","text":"A hiding,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"concealing, oneself:"},{"kind":"text","text":"(IAar, TA:) [or, accord. to analogy,"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"a mode,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"manner, of doing so."},{"kind":"text","text":"] ―         -b2-  See also"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"xamarN","text_ar":"خَمَرٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":". ―         -b3-"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"A mode, manner,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"way, of wearing the"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"ximaAr","text_ar":"خِمَار"},{"kind":"text","text":". (K, * TA.) You say,"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"A_in~ahaA laHasanapu Alximorapi","text_ar":"اـِنَّهَا لَحَسَنَةُ الخِمْرَةِ"},{"kind":"text","text":"["},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"Verily she has a beautiful mode of wearing the"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"xmAr","text_ar":"خمار"},{"kind":"text","text":"]. (S.) And hence the saying of 'Omar to Mo'áwiyeh,"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"maA A^a$obaha Eayonaka","text_ar":"مَا اَشْبَهَ عَيْنَكَ"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"biximorapi hinodK","text_ar":"بِخِمْرَةِ هِنْدٍ"},{"kind":"text","text":"["},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"How like is thine eye to Hind's"},{"kind":"text","text":"(when she practises her)"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"mode of wearing the"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"xmAr","text_ar":"خمار"},{"kind":"text","text":"!]. (TA.) Hence also, (TA,)"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"A_in~a AlEawaAna laA","text_ar":"اـِنَّ العَوَانَ لَا"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"tuEal~amu Alximorapa","text_ar":"تُعَلَّمُ الخِمْرَةَ"},{"kind":"text","text":"["},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"Verily she who has had a husband will not"},{"kind":"text","text":"require to"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"be taught the mode of wearing the"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"xmAr","text_ar":"خمار"},{"kind":"text","text":"]: (S, K, * TA:) a prov., (S, TA,) applied to him who is experienced and knowing: (K:) i. e. the experienced woman is not to be taught how she should act. (TA.)       -A2-  See also"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"xamorapN","text_ar":"خَمْرَةٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":"."}],"source_refs":["IAar","TA","S","K"]},{"entry_id":"n11481","headword_ar":"خَمَرَةٌ","root":"xmr","body":[{"kind":"text","text":": see"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"xamorapN","text_ar":"خَمْرَةٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":"."}],"source_refs":[]}]}}